<br>
The merchant's name is Elesseryl Terusser.  She's a high elf in an island tower in the Ocean of Tears.  Her location is positive 1307, negative 7883.  Check EQAtlas as well, I believe they list which island she is on (my maps are at home, I'm at work<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )<br>
